arm_group.description:
Intratumoral administration of RT-01 as single agent for patients with advanced solid tumors. The injection dose of RT-01 was determined by the lesion size:
mL for lesion length <1.5 cm;
mL for lesion length between 1.5 cm and 2.5 cm;
mL for lesion length between 2.5 cm and 5.0 cm;
mL for lesion length between >5 cm
